OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSir Lenny Henry to make    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FComic Relief farewell      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sir Lenny Henry is to host Comic Relief
OL,6, for the final time when the BBC        
OL,7, fundraising telethon returns in March. 
OL,9,FThe comedian, who co-founded the       
OL,10,Fcharity with director Richard Curtis in
OL,11,F1985, said it was time for "new faces" 
OL,12,Fafter nearly 40 years at the helm.     
OL,14,FThis year's campaign will culminate    
OL,15,Fwith the Red Nose Day broadcast on BBC 
OL,16,FOne on Friday 15 March.                
OL,18,F"I'm not going to be hosting any more  
OL,19,FComic Reliefs after this," he told BBC 
OL,20,FBreakfast on Wednesday.                
